ganga/python/GangaAtlas
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Athena:
-------
* New libdcap.so with improved read-ahead buffer tuning
  DQ2_LOCAL accesses on dCache should be significantly faster now
* Move FileStager configuration job option out of input.py and 
  prepend it in front of all user job options, providing workaround 
  for inputFilePeeker
* New extended dq2info.tar.gz tarball

Major rewrite of data handling of Athena/DQ2/LCG/Local
* Clean-up and new workflows in ganga-stange-in-out-dq2.py
  - New host detection algorithm based on DQ2_LOCAL_SITE_ID
  - Move all SE protocol detection to ToA.py file
  - Improve TURL generation algorithm and use bulk methods
    and more retries
  - Register output files already on worker node in DQ2
* Changes in DQ2OutputDataset
  - change DQ2OutputDataset in Athena/DQ2/LCG/Local workflow
    to register files already on worker node in DQ2
  - Output datasets are now based on sites and dataset names
    get space token name attached.
  - If a master job is split among several sites there are output
    dataset set per site created. These output datasets are attached
    to a container at the end of the master job
  - output datasets are frozen at the end of the master job
  - No empty dataset is created in AthenaLCGRTHandler or
    AthenaLocalRTHandler
  - config.DQ2.DQ2_LOCAL_SITE_ID should be set for a Local
    or Batch backend job

